Review: It has modern facility, relatively large campus, inspiring teachers, and hospitable staff. My journey here was a graceful experience. I learnt a lot, especially, communication, and critical thinking. I give only 3 stars because among all the wonderful lecturers, there exists a few old-fashioned teachers (who are spoiling the students with their bureaucratic and narrow-minded thinking). I really hope the school management had realized this issue and those people are no longer here.
